OL,3,C'I feel loved': Irish politician's
OL,4,CCork accent makes him a star in Jamaica
OL,6,FAn Irish politician has become a minor
OL,7,Fcelebrity in the Caribbean after many
OL,8,Fcompared his Cork accent to a Jamaican
OL,9,Fone.
OL,11,FThomas Gould, a Sinn Fein TD in the
OL,12,FIrish Parliament, has become well
OL,13,Fknown within the republic for is
OL,14,Fimpassioned speeches on a wide range
OL,15,Fof topics.
OL,17,FBut this fame has now crossed the
OL,18,FAtlantic after a clip of a recent
OL,19,Fspeech on the housing crisis in
OL,20,FIreland went viral in Jamaica,
OL,21,FBarbados, and other Caribbean nations.
OL,26,@sD@Wrr
