OL,3,C'I feel loved': Irish politician's
OL,4,CCork accent makes him a star in Jamaica
OL,6,FBut it wasn't the content of the
OL,7,Fspeech that pleased Jamaicans; it was
OL,8,Fhow he said it.
OL,10,FGould told the Jamaica Observer he had
OL,11,Fbeen contacted by "a mixture of the
OL,12,FIrish community, Jamaican and people
OL,13,Ffrom the Caribbean" who want him to
OL,14,Fvisit.
