PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772244190
OL,3,C'I feel loved': Irish politician's
OL,4,CCork accent makes him a star in Jamaica
OL,6,FHe said he "felt loved" by the
OL,7,Foutpouring but also said he didn't
OL,8,Fmind if people made a bit of fun of
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F"I know I have a very strong accent,
OL,12,Fand I know I speak very fast. So when
OL,13,FI listen to Jamaicans speak, not all
OL,14,Fof them, but some of them do speak
OL,15,Flike me."
OL,17,FGould said he had recently learned the
OL,18,Fmajority of Irish people who travelled
OL,19,Fto Jamaica came from Cork and Munster
OL,20,Fand brought their accents with them.
